In this article, President Xi of China and President Trump of the United States make remarks at the G20 summit in Osaka, Japan. President Xi mentions the historical significance of "Ping Pong Diplomacy" between China and the US, highlighting the importance of cooperation and dialogue. President Trump expresses his admiration for Chinese culture and emphasizes the need for a fair trade deal between the two countries. The article ends with a brief mention of a question about Huawei and the potential for a trade deal.